Title: Why is CHPT trading lower then BLNK?
Selftext: Title pretty much says it all, everything about CHPT seems better then BLNK especially when looking at global market share, so why is BLNK trading so much higher both price and trading volume then CHPT when CHPT the better stock IMO.

Title: What are your SpaceX moves? ARKX vs BPTRX vs SPCE vs GOOG vs waiting for SpaceX IPO to go public...
Selftext: I'm trying to figure out the best way to invest in SpaceX and I keep seeing so many varying opinions on it. (I've only been investing for less than a year, so I am still learning and looking to be educated.) I figured I'd wait until their IPO when public and then grab however many shares I could afford to lose. I own some Google and know they have about 9%, but some people are saying it's better to hold BPTRX or SPCE or ARKZ and I don't know enough about these companies to pick and choose. Or do I just chill out and wait for the SpaceX IPO and then buy whole shares? I want in on this Starlink stuff! I really appreciate you taking time to help me out.
